<h2><a name="a4">Assignment 4</a></h2>

<ul>
  <li><a href="a4/handout.pdf">Assignment handout (PDF)</a>
  <a href="a4/handout.ps">(PS)</a>
  <li>Due by 7:00pm inside drop box in BA 2220 on Thursday, August 10.<br>
  <li>Some people asked about the game of Amazons. Here are some pictures
  I stole from the Internet showing the initial state of the 10x10 game,
  a middle game state (illustrating a move), and an end game position
  (all the amazons are separated, assuming good play,
  so we can determine who will win).<br>
  <img src="a4/amazons-initial.gif" alt="Amazons initial game position">
  <img src="a4/amazons-ingame.gif" alt="Amazons in-game position">
  <li>Q1: Do not try to solve TSP in polynomial time (you proved that TSP
  is NP-complete on Test 2, so it's unlikely you'll be able to do it).
  Just show that TSP is polytime self-reducible.
  <li>Sample solutions:
  <a href="sol/A4sol.pdf">PDF</a> or
  <a href="sol/A4sol.ps">PS</a>
</ul>

